sequenceDiagram
    participant Platform as "Cloud Platform<br/>(ChatGPT/Claude/ElevenLabs)"
    participant Sidecar as "MCP Sidecar<br/>POST /mcp"
    participant AutoMem as "AutoMem API<br/>:8001"
    participant FalkorDB as "FalkorDB"
    participant Qdrant as "Qdrant"
    
    Note over Platform,Qdrant: Store Memory via Remote MCP
    
    Platform->>Sidecar: POST /mcp<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>{"method": "tools/call",<br/>"params": {"name": "store_memory"}}
    
    Sidecar->>Sidecar: Validate token<br/>Parse MCP JSON-RPC
    
    Sidecar->>AutoMem: POST /memory<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>{"content": "...", "tags": [...]}
    
    par Write to both databases
        AutoMem->>Qdrant: Store vector embedding
        AutoMem->>FalkorDB: Create memory node
    end
    
    AutoMem-->>Sidecar: {"memory_id": "abc123"}
    
    Sidecar-->>Platform: MCP JSON-RPC response<br/>{"result": {"memory_id": "abc123"}}
    
    Note over Platform,Qdrant: Recall Memory via Remote MCP
    
    Platform->>Sidecar: POST /mcp<br/>{"method": "tools/call",<br/>"params": {"name": "recall_memory"}}
    
    Sidecar->>AutoMem: GET /recall<br/>?query=...&tags=...
    
    par Parallel queries
        AutoMem->>Qdrant: Vector similarity search
        AutoMem->>FalkorDB: Keyword + tag filtering
    end
    
    AutoMem-->>Sidecar: [{"id": "...", "content": "..."}]
    
    Sidecar-->>Platform: MCP JSON-RPC response<br/>{"result": {"memories": [...]}}